div.p: UC - Upstream connection failure UF - Upstream connection termination UO - Upstream overflow (circuit breaker) UR - Upstream request timeout
NR - No route configured NC - No cluster found DI - Delay injected (fault injection) FI - Abort injected (fault injection)
UAEX - Unauthorized (external auth) RLSE - Rate limited DC - Downstream connection termination
- - No flags (success) LR - Local reply (Envoy generated)
